        "name": "Retrospective observational study of clinical VAD pump returns",
        "description": "Hemolysis data were collected retrospectively from pumps returned to the manufacturer following explant or device exchange. No experimental manipulation of operating conditions was performed; conditions were inferred post hoc from implant logs. The study was not pre-registered and randomisation was not possible. Data collection followed ISO 10993-4 haemocompatibility guidance for observational contexts.",
